nodes.text: Dorin was a planet located in the galaxy's Expansion Region that was the homeworld of the Kel Dor species. Its Dorin gas and helium-rich environment meant that they were forced to rely on rebreathers to survive off-world, as oxygen was deadly to them. During the Clone Wars, Jedi General Anakin Skywalker and Commander Ahsoka Tano routed Separatist forces near Dorin.
